Shark.io for Chrome Extension is an exciting and thrilling game inspired by the classic Snake game. You can play it for free on the website https://googlesnake.org/.

In this game, you take control of a hungry shark and your objective is to become bigger by devouring sea creatures and unsuspecting beachgoers. As you consume them, your shark grows in size, allowing you to become more formidable. However, you must be cautious and avoid being eaten by larger sharks that roam the waters.

"Shark.io" delivers a thrilling gameplay experience with a touch of intensity. The game features a realistic depiction of the food chain, and whenever you successfully catch and eat a fish or a human, blood is displayed, adding to the game's immersive atmosphere.

To play "Shark.io," simply visit the website https://googlesnake.org/ using your web browser. Dive into the ocean, control your shark's movements, and strategically hunt down your prey while evading larger predators. It's a test of your reflexes, strategy, and survival skills.
